articles.title: US College Students To Land First Robotic Rover on Moon, Before NASA - LatestLY
articles.description: The mission, likely to be launched this spring, represents America's first robotic Moon rover, as well as the first rover developed by university students. NASA's first robotic Moon rover - VIPER rover -- is scheduled to launch only next year.
